pageContext.claim: “CNN called a San Diego news station (@KUSINews) for negative reports on the Wall. When the station said that Walls work, CNN no longer had interest. #FakeNews”
pageContext.analysis: Trump seized on a story circulating on the right that CNN did not proceed with an interview with a reporter at San Diego's KUSI station because it did not fit CNN's "narrative." CNN denied that, saying the story plans changed. The executive at the television station that accused CNN later conceded he didn't really know why the network turned him down.
